-- Citigroup Global Markets Joins as Energy Clearing Member of ECC
-- B y   R a c h e l   M o r i s o n
-- 2012-10-02T10:42:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-02/citigroup-global-markets-joins-as-energy-clearing-member-of-ecc.html
Citigroup Global Markets Ltd. joined
European Commodity Clearing AG as a general clearing member.  Citigroup can settle its own transactions, customer
transactions and is available for non-clearing members as a
service provider, ECC said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Morison in  London  at 
 rmorison@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Lars Paulsson at 
 lpaulsson@bloomberg.net  